  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Surgical resection is the only potential curative treatment available for renal cell
      carcinoma. The purpose of this study is to clarify the surgical and oncologic outcomes of
      laparoendoscopic single-site radical nephrectomy for localized Renal Cell Carcinoma.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
